X-Men crossed over with the animated series Spider-Man, when Spider-Man seeks out the X-Men\'s help to stave off his progressing mutation. In the abbreviated form of the Secret Wars storyline, the Beyonder and Madame Web selected Spider-Man to lead a team of heroes including Storm against a group of villains. An earlier draft of \"Secret Wars\" involved all of the X-Men, but transporting the voice cast to Los Angeles where production for the Spider-Man animated series was based from Canada had been too costly in previous crossovers, so the episode was re-written to include only Storm, whose actress, Iona Morris, lived in Los Angeles.[9][10] Hulk and She-Hulk were excluded from the episodes because the Incredible Hulk animated series .
